x4freetext: *By authors*.Gamma-activity of some aluminum foils
has been measured and cross sections  Na-22  production
was  calculated. Calculated  cross sections have been
compared with Martens and Schweimer data (see  Rel-Ref)
to check the method of  absolute  cross  section
measurements.
The errors include:
* statistical errors,
* error in the target thickness,
The error in the calibration of spectrometer.
The uncertainty of beam current.
The uncertainty of deuteron energy.
